Steps to run SVTB Lintra

Clone RTL/VC, source ep/rtr and compile like how you would before running a test

cd $IP_ROOT/tools/svtb_lintra
source run_svtb_lintra

Only after you run svtb lintra, you ll see the tb_top_violations.xml file. Get the path to the file.
For gui:
$LINTRA/bin/lintra_gui -ov <path to tb_top_violations.xml>

E.g.
$LINTRA/bin/lintra_gui -ov /nfs/fm/disks/fm_infrach_00027/vnandaku/12_28_ep_svtb/ip-iosf-sideband-rtl/results/tests/svtb_lint/_nfs_fm_disks_fm_infrach_00027_vnandaku_12_28_ep_svtb_ip-iosf-sideband-rtl_verif_tests_svtb_sbendpoint/tb_top_violations.xml
